
Installation
============

1) Create base directory
   $ mkdir .ansible
2) Create directory .ansible/roles
   $ mkdir .ansible/roles
3) Clone vbotka.ansible
   $ git clone https://github.com/vbotka/ansible-ansible .ansible/roles/vbotka.ansible
4) Copy contrib/workbench to ansible-misc
   $ cp -r .ansible/roles/vbotka.ansible/contrib/workbench .ansible/ansible-misc
5) Create link to ansible-misc
   $ cd .ansible && ln -s ansible-misc misc

